# Wine Cellar Universe - Sample UI Output

This directory contains sample UI files generated by Phase Î©-III for the wine_cellar universe.

## Generated Files

1. `page.tsx` - Hub page (main entry point)
2. `dashboard-page.tsx` - Dashboard with stats
3. `detail-page.tsx` - Item detail view
4. `tools-page.tsx` - AI tools interface
5. `workflows-page.tsx` - Workflow management
6. `ItemCard.tsx` - Reusable item card component

These files demonstrate the automatic UI generation capabilities of the UX Auto-Scaffolder.
